This assignment is about adding the code to drive the pc.
The pc moves related to the user's input.

7|y = upper left
8|k = up
9|u = upper right
6|l = right
3|n = lower right
2|j = lower down
1|b = lower left
4|h = left

> = entering the building while standing on the building.
< = exit from the building.

5|space|. = rest

t = trainer list. Displaying the symbol and the relative position
up arrow = scroll up the trainer list
down arrow = scroll down the trainer list
escape = return to the trainer control

Q = quit the game

Trainer will move like sentry after the battle.
The pc will get out the pokemart or pokecenter right after it enter to the building and see the message.
It can move right after without pressing <.
